# Agent working directories
.auto-claude/
.claude/

# Python (not part of Flutter project) — stray scripts, venvs, tooling spew.
# Repo tooling under scripts/ is exempt: it is version-controlled and CI runs it.
# Without this exception `git add -A` drops it SILENTLY — that is how
# scripts/check-schema-refs.py was committed as a CI job with no script behind it.
*.py
!scripts/*.py

